data.description: Welcome to your country dream home! This remarkable four bedroom, two bath sanctuary combines rustic elegance with modern comfort. Featuring a prominent wooden beam in the living room, wood burning fireplace, high ceilings all throughout, white easy close cabinets and drawers, granite countertops, and custom finishes, this home exudes sophistication. Enjoy the peaceful country setting and spacious backyard with 1.4 acres of amazing possibilities. On this property you'll find several mature trees, wild flowers, and even walking paths that were cleared out to enjoy this beautiful serene property! Schedule a showing today and make this your perfect rural retreat!
